Header: LIVE: UNP working committee meeting begins
Content: Colombo (News 1st): The United National Party Working Committee meeting began at Temple Trees a short while ago. The meeting is being chaired by Prime Minister  Ranil Wickramasinghe. BREAKING NEWS – එක්සත් ජාතික පක්ෂ කෘත්‍යධිකාරි මණ්ඩල රැස්වීම අරලියගහ මන්දිරයේදී ඇරඹෙයි Posted by Newsfirst.lk on Wednesday, July 31, 2019
